STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Cross-Respondent,
v.
Tyrone STRODE a/k/a Tyrone Davis, Tyrone Davisstrode, Tyrone S. Davis-Strode, Turpme S. Davis and Eric S. Pettersson, Defendant-Cross-Petitioner. C-1006 September Term 2016
079230 Supreme Court of New Jersey. June 1, 2018

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A cross-petition for certification of the judgment in A-005418-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the cross-petition for certification is denied.
